I'm going to say no to a homosexual relationship for now, Minime. There are 
quite a few people in the RPG who are set severely against that. If, however, 
no one has any problem with it, I'll repeal my decition.

As to Bob Skir, I can't believe this is actually happening! I didn't think 
that we were this important! He's welcome to email me, but how do we know its 
the real him?

::Ramulus::

Ramulus spins around, his hand on his gun as he looks at the trainers. His 
eyes narrow as he sees Spears in their grip.

Ramulus takes a few steps forward, watching the enemy carefully. He reaches 
into a compartment with his free arm, bringing out a device.

"I have a holo-map right here," he yells over to them, holding up the device, 
"I'll exchange it for Spears. I'll still meet you for Striker, though, if you 
wish. You can return him to me then."
